---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<section class="bg-[#0f172a] text-white">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 sm:py-24">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
      Most contractor software reviews are useless.<br />
      <span class="text-[#22c55e]">These aren't.</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed">
      No vendor copy. No padding. Just an honest call on what each tool costs, what it gets right, and who it's actually wrong for — written for contractors running 1–50 people, not enterprise.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8">Most Read Reviews</h2>
  <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">Not sure where to start? These are the ones contractors look up most.</p>
  
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
    <!-- Jobber -->
    <a href="/blog/jobber-review/" class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-5 hover:border-[#0f172a] hover:shadow-md transition">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#e0f2fe] rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-lg font-bold text-[#0369a1]">J</div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold group-hover:text-[#0f172a]">Jobber Review</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">From $49/mo</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">The best all-around field service software for contractors running 1–25 employees.</p>
      <div class="mt-3 flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="text-xs bg-[#dcfce7] text-[#166534] px-2 py-1 rounded">⭐ Top Pick</span>
        <span class="text-xs bg-[#fef3c7] text-[#92400e] px-2 py-1 rounded">8.8/10</span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <!-- Housecall Pro -->
    <a href="/blog/housecall-pro-review/" class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-5 hover:border-[#0f172a] hover:shadow-md transition">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#fce7f3] rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-lg font-bold text-[#be185d]">H</div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold group-hover:text-[#0f172a]">Housecall Pro Review</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">From $65/mo</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Best mobile app in the category. Built-in review requests on most plans.</p>
      <div class="mt-3 flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="text-xs bg-[#dcfce7] text-[#166534] px-2 py-1 rounded">Strong Pick</span>
        <span class="text-xs bg-[#fef3c7] text-[#92400e] px-2 py-1 rounded">8.4/10</span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <!-- ServiceTitan -->
    <a href="/blog/servicetitan-review/" class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-5 hover:border-[#0f172a] hover:shadow-md transition">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#e2e8f0] rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-lg font-bold text-[#475569]">ST</div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold group-hover:text-[#0f172a]">ServiceTitan Review</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">From $398/mo</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Enterprise-grade for contractors doing $1M+ in revenue with 10+ employees.</p>
      <div class="mt-3 flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="text-xs bg-[#e2e8f0] text-[#475569] px-2 py-1 rounded">Specialist</span>
        <span class="text-xs bg-[#fef3c7] text-[#92400e] px-2 py-1 rounded">7.9/10</span>
      </div>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Head-to-Head Comparisons</h2>
  <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">Deciding between two tools? These cut straight to the call.</p>
  
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
    <a href="/blog/jobber-vs-housecall-pro/" class="group flex items-center gap-4 p-5 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:border-[#0f172a] hover:shadow-md transition">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-[#e0f2fe] rounded flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold text-[#0369a1]">J</div>
        <span class="text-gray-400">vs</span>
        <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-[#fce7f3] rounded flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold text-[#be185d]">H</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="font-semibold group-hover:text-[#0f172a]">Jobber vs Housecall Pro</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Best for most vs best mobile app</p>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/blog/servicetitan-vs-jobber/" class="group flex items-center gap-4 p-5 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:border-[#0f172a] hover:shadow-md transition">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-[#e2e8f0] rounded flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold text-[#475569]">ST</div>
        <span class="text-gray-400">vs</span>
        <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-[#e0f2fe] rounded flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold text-[#0369a1]">J</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="font-semibold group-hover:text-[#0f172a]">ServiceTitan vs Jobber</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Enterprise vs small team</p>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/blog/housecall-pro-vs-fieldedge/" class="group flex items-center gap-4 p-5 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:border-[#0f172a] hover:shadow-md transition">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-[#fce7f3] rounded flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold text-[#be185d]">H</div>
        <span class="text-gray-400">vs</span>
        <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-[#fef3c7] rounded flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold text-[#92400e]">FE</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="font-semibold group-hover:text-[#0f172a]">Housecall Pro vs FieldEdge</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Easy setup vs QuickBooks depth</p>
      </div>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Best Software by Trade</h2>
  
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
    <a href="/blog/hvac-software/" class="group p-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:border-[#0f172a] hover:shadow-md transition">
      <p class="font-semibold group-hover:text-[#0f172a]">HVAC Software</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">7 options that actually work</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/blog/plumbing-software/" class="group p-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:border-[#0f172a] hover:shadow-md transition">
      <p class="font-semibold group-hover:text-[#0f172a]">Plumbing Software</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">5 options for small business</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/blog/roofing-software/" class="group p-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:border-[#0f172a] hover:shadow-md transition">
      <p class="font-semibold group-hover:text-[#0f172a]">Roofing Software</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">5 options compared</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/blog/landscaping-software/" class="group p-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:border-[#0f172a] hover:shadow-md transition">
      <p class="font-semibold group-hover:text-[#0f172a]">Landscaping Software</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">6 options reviewed</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/blog/pest-control-software/" class="group p-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:border-[#0f172a] hover:shadow-md transition">
      <p class="font-semibold group-hover:text-[#0f172a]">Pest Control Software</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">5 options that work</p>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-[#f8fafc] border-t border-b border-gray-200">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">The work behind the call</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mb-6">
      Most contractor software reviews skip the hard part. Here's what actually goes into each one on this site.
    </p>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="p-5 bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">We sign up for trials</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Every tool gets tested hands-on, not just reviewed from a vendor demo.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-5 bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">We analyze pricing honestly</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Real pricing, including hidden fees and contract terms that vendors don't advertise.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-5 bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">We read hundreds of reviews</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">G2, Capterra, and industry forums to find patterns in real contractor feedback.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Best Software by Category</h2>
  
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
    <a href="/blog/best-estimating-software-small-contractors/" class="group p-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:border-[#0f172a] hover:shadow-md transition">
      <p class="font-semibold group-hover:text-[#0f172a]">Estimating Software (Small)</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Best for small contractors</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/blog/best-scheduling-software-contractors/" class="group p-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:border-[#0f172a] hover:shadow-md transition">
      <p class="font-semibold group-hover:text-[#0f172a]">Scheduling Software</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">6 best options for contractors</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/blog/best-crm-contractors/" class="group p-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:border-[#0f172a] hover:shadow-md transition">
      <p class="font-semibold group-hover:text-[#0f172a]">CRM for Contractors</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Best customer management tools</p>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

